# kwrite

> Text editor of the KDE Desktop project
> See also kate
> More information: https://apps.kde.org/kwrite/

- Open a text file:

`kwrite {file value}`

- Open multiple text files:

`kwrite {string value: file1 file2 ...}`

- Open a text file with a specific encoding:

`kwrite --encoding={string value: UTF-8} {file value}`

- Open a text file and navigate to a specific line and column:

`kwrite --line {string value: line_number} --column {string value: column_number} {file value}`
